ssion, phylogeny, and biology in mammals. Moreover, the link between genetic variability of\n              Pneumocystis\n              isolated from populations of the same bat species and their geographic area could be exploited in terms of phylogeography.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Akbar, Haroon", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Pin\u00e7on, Claire", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Aliouat-Denis, Cecile-Marie", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Derouiche, Sandra", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Taylor, Maria-Lucia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Pottier, Muriel", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Carreto-Binaghi, Laura-Helena", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gonz\u00e1lez-Gonz\u00e1lez, Antonio E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Courpon, Aurore", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Barriel, V\u00e9ronique", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Guillot, Jacques", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chab\u00e9, Magali", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Suarez-Alvarez, Roberto O.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Aliouat, El Moukhtar", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Dei-Cas, Eduardo", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Demanche, Christine", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/4a982d6cbcb2e9e2601cc4425c496e05", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/1f08319b8fe54007fa7a3c95ca2fbf0523d465401dc5070dfb4f711982d58c4d", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/6Z6FCTN2", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/6Z6FCTN2", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/77e980e9a00bf62e2ed18143fd461f2f!/b14764-17315", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relat